        "@value": "LE CRIME DE L'ORIENT-EXPRESS - par Agatha Christie"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>\n<b>The legendary Murder on the Orient Express comes to life on stage in Quebec.</b><br><br>\n\nImmerse yourself in the fascinating world of the Queen of Crime, Agatha Christie, with one of the most iconic cases featuring the legendary Hercule Poirot!<br><br>\n\n With heart-pounding suspense and touches of humor, Murder on the Orient Express takes you on a high-speed journey where every passenger hides a secret. Get ready for a captivating performance, where every glance, every detail, brings you a little closer to the truth. Experience the intensity of a thrilling closed-door mystery, where the intrigue deepens with every passing moment. With twists and unexpected revelations, this unmissable masterpiece by Agatha Christie will keep you on the edge of your seat until the very end. <br><br>\n\nAboard the legendary Orient Express, traveling from Istanbul to Calais, an inexplicable murder is committed, followed by an assassination attempt. Faced with this complex mystery, Hercule Poirot puts his famous 'little gray cells' to the test to separate fact from fiction. The audience is invited to step into the shoes of a detective, gathering clues and false leads throughout the show.<br><br>\n\nAuthor: Agatha Christie<br><br>\n\nAdaptation: Ken Ludwig<br>\nTranslation and Direction: Martin Lavigne<br>\nProduced by: Productions La Comédie Humaine<br>\nLighting, Video, and Set Design: Les studios XF-40 (David Lavallée-Gagné):<br>\nOriginal music and soundtrack design: Medhat Hanbali<br>\nAssistant director, technical director, stage manager, and sound operator: Mélanie Bouffard<br>\nPhoto credit: Hugo B. Lefort<br>\nGraphic design: Jérémie St-Cyr<br>\nRunning time: 90 minutes (performance without intermission)<br><br>\n\n\n<i><small>© 2016 Agatha Christie Limited & Ken Ludwig, adapté de Murder on The Orient-Express © 1934 Agatha Christie Limited. Tous droits réservés. ®MURDER ON THE ORIENT EXPRESS, AGATHA CHRISTIE et POIROT sont des marques déposées d'Agatha Christie Limited au Royaume-Uni et ailleurs. Tous droits réservés.</i></small></p>\n\n\n\n<style>\n\n.pricelevel-price-temp-to {display: none;}\n.pricelevel-price-temp-pricemax {display: none;}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\ntw-seats-selectes-plv{display: none !important;}\n</style>\n"
      }
    ],
